data.description: Welcome to the home of your dreams!  Discover rural tranquility in this spacious 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, thoughtfully updated since 2016 for modern comfort in a serene setting.  Step inside to find a warm, contemporary interior boasting a new furnace and home generator for year-round coziness and peace of mind. The newly installed siding ensures durability, while an on-demand water heater guarantees endless hot water convenience.  Outside, your private oasis awaits with a refreshing pool, complemented by a charming gazebo—a perfect spot for relaxation or gatherings. Inside, revel in new carpeting, and make use of the versatile den addition to suit your lifestyle needs.  A concrete drive leads to a spacious garage, offering ample parking and storage options. Embrace the scenic beauty of this rural escape in a close-knit community.  Step out back in the private fenced yard and relax under the gazebo or take a dip in the pool. Plug in your RV on the extra pad to the side of the garage!  Don't miss out!  Seize the opportunity to own this meticulously updated home—a haven of comfort nestled in a picturesque rural landscape.
